        <h1>Video Production in Switzerland: Why Leading Brands Choose Zurich</h1>
        <p class="lead">Switzerland has a reputation for precision, and film production is no exception. Within the country, Zurich has established itself as the hub where the best talent, infrastructure, and brands demanding international-grade quality all converge.</p>
        <p class="post-meta"><span>Viven Team</span> <span>·</span> <span>July 21, 2026</span></p>
